    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-06-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-06-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="297" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d297">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">[Telegram]</note>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Campbell</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-06-15">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">June</hi> 15, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It is important that the minister to Mexico should proceed at once. Your
                            resignation will, therefore, be accepted, with thanks for your service
                            and regret for your retirement. Communicate by telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lewis D. Campell,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c., New Orleans.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
